window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>From Ian and Charlotte’s first meeting in Paris to a look into the future, <i>Taggart Family Values</i> chronicles Masters and Mercenaries’ favorite family through a series of short stories and novellas. Includes one brand new short story and one new novella. Lexi hopes listeners will have a blast connecting with Ian and Charlotte and all their little monsters! </p> <p><i>Taggart Family Values</i> includes the novellas <i>Paradise City</i>, <i>Sweet Child o’ Mine</i>, <i>Homecoming</i>, and <i>Countdown</i>. It also includes the short stories \"Adam Tells All\", \"Make Lemonade\", \"Rough Night\", and \"Stuck at the Office\". </p> <p>Some of the stories were previously published in newsletters and cookbooks. </p>"; 
